===Particle===
[[Category:Japanese particles]]
'''まで''' ([[made]])

#[[until]], [[till]]
#* 10時まで働くつもりだ。
#*:10じまではたらくつもりだ。
#*:10 ji made hataraku tsumori da.
#*:I'll be working until 10 o'clock.

<!-- From -まで page -->
====Usage note====
まで is often combined with [[から]] (''[[kara]]'', ''from'') to provide a range of something (e.g., time or distance).  This results in a construction like　三時'''から'''五時'''まで''' (さんじ'''から'''ごじ'''まで''', ''san-ji '''kara''' go-ji '''made''''', '''''from''' 3 o'clock '''until''' 5 o'clock'').